(CYA all tomorrow.)

Brix finally came out from under the CR Chambers.

"Well, that's the best I can do for now. They're all at 80% power. 
Hopefull when we get the parts from my ship we can bring them up 
fully.(Brix than goes over to the CR Chamber Fliq is in.)You my 
friend, though, will have to stay the night because yours is still at 
40% power. I didn't want to risk hurting you. Hurting you as Bronco 
is one thing. Hurting you as Brix is another. I know you can't here 
me, but I'm so sorry. I have to learn to control him. But, I'll see 
you in the morning."

Brix waks down to his quarters. It is almost destroyed.

"Damn it! How am I supposed to rest here!?! Well, I'll go keep Fliq 
company."

Brix enters the bridge and goes over to the side with the least 
amount of soot. He lies down.

"G'night Fliq."
